overview:
Liam Ryan is CEO & Cofounder at GetHealth, an NDRC Launchpad alum (Irelands #1 startup accelerator). He is a skilled musician, teacher and engineer, embarking on adventures as an online entrepreneur. He has been selected as one of Ireland’s top technology and startup leaders.

Liam love’s his health, and he wants you to love your health too. He believes there is a need for a personality that will act as a catalyst for people to engage in their health. What Steve Jobs did for technology is now needed for the health industry. Liam is working hard to change people’s lives, and give them the tools that they need for that to become a reality.

Specialties Setting Goals, Hard Work, Achieving Goals
